transcripts.text: Stephen Darby Ministries presents a two-day Miami conference featuring Minister Missy Darby and the Destined Ministry Prayer and Praise Team Thursday, August 1st, 2019 at 7 p.m.  and.  Saturday, August 3rd, 2019 at 1 p.m The Embassy Suites by Hilton Miami International Airport.  Registration fee of $25 covers both days.  Children 12 and under are free.  The Embassy Suites by Hilton Miami International Airport is located at 3974 Northwest South River Drive, Miami, Florida 33142.  For more information, please visit us at www.stephendarveeministries.com or give us a call at 502-907-5579.
